  [ Andreas Loibl ]
  * New method to add cdrom/ floppy devices to fstab (from
    initscripts-kanotix-live).
  * Make sure that /proc exists on root-partition.
  * Don't backup Knoppix specific Xsession file (45xsession) anymore.
  * changed some update-rc.d-commands.
  * minor bugfixes.

  [ Joerg Schirottke ]
  * Added rest of etch's update-rc.d-commands.

 -- Joerg Schirottke <master@kanotix.com>  Fri, 15 Sep 2006 03:27:23 +0200

