  * changed qtparted to gparted.

 -- Andreas Loibl <andreas@andreas-loibl.de>  Sat,  9 Sep 2006 22:12:09 +0200

knx-installer (0.4.0.22) experimental; urgency=low

  * fixed --non-interactive and --installer option.
  * added "&>/dev/null" to update-rc.d-commands (splashy, acpi-support).
  * changed some update-rc.d-commands (alsa-utils, udev, single, hwclock.sh,
    hwclockfirst.sh).

 -- Andreas Loibl <andreas@andreas-loibl.de>  Sun,  6 Aug 2006 22:29:11 +0200

knx-installer (0.4.0.21) experimental; urgency=low

  * added --installer option (similar to --non-interactive, but with
    bootdisk-creation enabled)
  * added KDM-AutoLogin as a new installer module
  * updated kopt-line.
  * activation of powersaved, splashy, acpi-support after hd-install.
  * updated /etc/host template.

 -- Andreas Loibl <andreas@andreas-loibl.de>  Fri,  4 Aug 2006 22:20:04 +0200

knx-installer (0.4.0.20) experimental; urgency=low

  * knoppix --> kanotix transtion part 1, thanks to RoEn.
  * knoppix --> kanotix transtion part 2, thanks to x-un-i.
  * transition knoppix-{autoconfig,halt,reboot} to
    live-{{autoconfig,halt,reboot}
  * don't depend directly on kudzu, use initscripts-kanotix-live instead.
  * quick'n'dirty hotfix for knoppix-hd-autoconfig.

